1
00:01:39,560 --> 00:01:43,270
[Road to Success]

2
00:01:44,690 --> 00:01:47,850
[Episode 28]

3
00:01:49,120 --> 00:01:50,680
Long time no see, Ms. Lin.

4
00:01:52,009 --> 00:01:53,009
Director Qian.

5
00:01:53,030 --> 00:01:55,160
I must apologize to you and the school.

6
00:01:56,080 --> 00:01:57,990
If the school decides to discipline me,

7
00:01:57,990 --> 00:02:00,250
I will accept whatever decision is made.

8
00:02:01,510 --> 00:02:03,210
Actually, according to
the school's regulations,

9
00:02:03,210 --> 00:02:04,720
being absent from work for 3 days

10
00:02:04,720 --> 00:02:06,180
is grounds for dismissal.

11
00:02:06,590 --> 00:02:07,450
Director Qian.

12
00:02:07,720 --> 00:02:09,050
I don't have to return to my post,

13
00:02:09,050 --> 00:02:10,120
but please allow me

14
00:02:10,120 --> 00:02:12,800
to continue serving as
the football team supervisor.

15
00:02:12,800 --> 00:02:14,230
I'm willing to work for free.

16
00:02:14,230 --> 00:02:15,600
How is that possible?

17
00:02:15,620 --> 00:02:17,160
Think about it, how could the school

18
00:02:17,160 --> 00:02:19,070
hire someone
who isn't a teacher at the school

19
00:02:19,070 --> 00:02:20,600
to serve as the supervisor?

20
00:02:22,570 --> 00:02:23,620
However,

21
00:02:24,960 --> 00:02:26,690
you didn't actually skip work.

22
00:02:27,120 --> 00:02:28,579
You filed a leave request.

23
00:02:32,110 --> 00:02:32,680
Right, right.

24
00:02:32,680 --> 00:02:33,310
Here.

25
00:02:33,440 --> 00:02:34,200
Look,

26
00:02:34,470 --> 00:02:35,470
I even signed it.

27
00:02:34,970 --> 00:02:35,510
[Request for Leave for Teachers of
Hongjing No. 8 High]

28
00:02:35,530 --> 00:02:36,329
[Dear Director, I'm writing to request
19 days of leave due to health issues.]

29
00:02:36,350 --> 00:02:36,900
[I kindly ask for your approval.
Thank you.]

30
00:02:36,910 --> 00:02:37,650
[Person Covering Duties: Wang Fa]
[Applicant: Lin Wanxing]

31
00:02:38,230 --> 00:02:39,070
Wang Fa...

32
00:02:40,840 --> 00:02:42,680
Having a family member fill out
the leave request for you

33
00:02:42,680 --> 00:02:44,940
isn't a serious violation of principle.

34
00:02:45,620 --> 00:02:46,870
Ms. Lin.

35
00:02:46,930 --> 00:02:48,370
Just go back to work

36
00:02:48,400 --> 00:02:49,850
once you recover.

37
00:02:54,240 --> 00:02:55,700
Thank you, Director Qian.

38
00:03:02,190 --> 00:03:04,430
[Dear Director Qian. With the exams
approaching, the team urgently needs...]

39
00:03:07,520 --> 00:03:09,400
So Qian also reads poems?

40
00:03:07,570 --> 00:03:08,370
[If I can stop one heart from breaking,]

41
00:03:08,390 --> 00:03:09,560
[I shall not live in vain.]

42
00:03:17,960 --> 00:03:18,840
Director Qian.

43
00:03:19,680 --> 00:03:22,640
Can I borrow a book from you?

44
00:03:23,840 --> 00:03:24,750
A book?

45
00:03:25,079 --> 00:03:26,079
What book?

46
00:03:28,760 --> 00:03:30,620
That red poetry collection.

47
00:03:36,710 --> 00:03:37,400
Sure.

48
00:03:37,910 --> 00:03:39,680
I'm all for

49
00:03:39,680 --> 00:03:41,010
young people reading.

50
00:03:41,290 --> 00:03:42,050
Here you are.

51
00:03:41,690 --> 00:03:42,750
[The Complete Poems of Emily Dickinson]

52
00:03:44,840 --> 00:03:45,680
Thank you.

53
00:03:52,960 --> 00:03:54,360
It's so nice

54
00:03:54,360 --> 00:03:55,640
to have Ms. Lin back.

55
00:03:55,940 --> 00:03:57,800
Even this cucumber tastes sweet.

56
00:03:57,910 --> 00:04:00,110
I wonder what Ms. Lin wants to see us for.

57
00:04:00,280 --> 00:04:01,120
Guys.

58
00:04:01,400 --> 00:04:02,520
Ms. Lin.

59
00:04:02,840 --> 00:04:04,170
Thank you for the fruit.

60
00:04:04,910 --> 00:04:06,800
I just went to Director Qian's office

61
00:04:06,800 --> 00:04:08,840
and borrowed a poetry collection from him.

62
00:04:08,840 --> 00:04:09,710
Look.

63
00:04:09,710 --> 00:04:11,180
There's a dog-eared corner on this page

64
00:04:11,180 --> 00:04:12,640
of the poetry collection.

65
00:04:13,230 --> 00:04:13,640
[If I can stop one heart from breaking,]

66
00:04:13,660 --> 00:04:14,070
[I shall not live in vain.]

67
00:04:14,820 --> 00:04:16,589
This looks familiar.

68
00:04:17,120 --> 00:04:19,600
Isn't this the poem from the fax?

69
00:04:17,930 --> 00:04:18,610
[If I can ease one life the aching,]

70
00:04:18,630 --> 00:04:19,430
[or cool one pain,]

71
00:04:22,070 --> 00:04:24,070
So the mystery person is Qian?

72
00:04:28,420 --> 00:04:29,750
But that can't be right.

73
00:04:29,790 --> 00:04:31,390
The writing on my football lending card

74
00:04:31,390 --> 00:04:32,430
was handwritten,

75
00:04:32,430 --> 00:04:34,510
and it doesn't match his handwriting.

76
00:04:34,510 --> 00:04:36,170
I was thinking about that too.

77
00:04:40,390 --> 00:04:42,120
Let's go over everything
from the beginning together.

78
00:04:42,120 --> 00:04:43,510
First,

79
00:04:43,510 --> 00:04:46,280
we found the football lending card
in Chen Jianghe's desk drawer,

80
00:04:46,280 --> 00:04:48,180
then the crossword puzzle

81
00:04:48,200 --> 00:04:49,960
in Qin Ao's desk drawer.

82
00:04:49,990 --> 00:04:51,840
And finally

83
00:04:51,860 --> 00:04:53,320
that map in my desk drawer.

84
00:04:55,690 --> 00:04:57,700
So these clues prove

85
00:04:58,159 --> 00:04:59,560
that whoever wrote the note
on the football lending card

86
00:04:59,560 --> 00:05:00,870
must know us very well.

87
00:05:03,160 --> 00:05:04,480
I agree.

88
00:05:07,830 --> 00:05:09,830
But who could it be?

89
00:05:14,930 --> 00:05:16,490
I think

90
00:05:17,430 --> 00:05:19,160
I may have figured out who it is.

91
00:05:22,310 --> 00:05:25,070
I'm going to go ask Director Qian
for a straight answer.

92
00:05:25,070 --> 00:05:26,000
Do you guys know

93
00:05:26,000 --> 00:05:28,380
where he usually goes after school?

94
00:05:29,070 --> 00:05:30,360
To Hongyang Park to play chess.

95
00:05:30,360 --> 00:05:32,220
Rain or shine, he never misses it.

96
00:05:35,360 --> 00:05:36,040
Check.

97
00:05:40,000 --> 00:05:41,680
-Corner knight check.
-Grandma, look.

98
00:05:41,680 --> 00:05:43,610
-I know how to ride it.
-Be careful.

99
00:05:43,630 --> 00:05:45,950
Darn it, a corner knight check followed by
a cannon.

100
00:05:45,950 --> 00:05:46,720
Unbeatable.

101
00:05:46,720 --> 00:05:47,390
You're done for.

102
00:05:47,390 --> 00:05:48,240
I'm done playing with you.

103
00:05:48,240 --> 00:05:49,950
I'm going home
to take care of my grandson.

104
00:05:49,950 --> 00:05:50,630
I'm done playing with you.

105
00:05:50,630 --> 00:05:51,630
You're running off after just one game?

106
00:05:51,630 --> 00:05:52,890
You still owe me a meal.

107
00:05:53,480 --> 00:05:54,940
Let's continue tomorrow.

108
00:05:57,310 --> 00:05:58,310
Ms. Lin.

109
00:05:59,260 --> 00:06:00,120
Director Qian.

110
00:06:00,560 --> 00:06:01,930
Let me play

111
00:06:01,970 --> 00:06:03,330
this game with you.

112
00:06:03,360 --> 00:06:04,880
That would be great.

113
00:06:04,900 --> 00:06:05,510
Come on.

114
00:06:12,310 --> 00:06:13,040
You go first.

115
00:06:19,720 --> 00:06:20,630
Knight jump.

116
00:06:23,430 --> 00:06:25,390
Did you come to see me
about something, Ms. Lin?

117
00:06:25,390 --> 00:06:26,390
Director Qian.

118
00:06:27,240 --> 00:06:28,750
Thank you

119
00:06:29,720 --> 00:06:30,720
for everything.

120
00:06:31,220 --> 00:06:32,100
Thank me?

121
00:06:32,120 --> 00:06:33,930
I haven't done anything to deserve it.

122
00:06:33,930 --> 00:06:35,630
If you have something to say, just say it.

123
00:06:35,630 --> 00:06:37,680
Letting me come to work at Hongjing

124
00:06:37,770 --> 00:06:39,390
and become the football team supervisor,

125
00:06:39,390 --> 00:06:41,320
helping the team get reorganized—

126
00:06:41,390 --> 00:06:45,600
which one of these things wasn't something
you helped with behind the scenes?

127
00:06:45,600 --> 00:06:46,670
Am I right?

128
00:06:49,240 --> 00:06:50,520
Elaborate on that.

129
00:06:53,790 --> 00:06:56,040
Stuffing a colorful box
filled with puzzles

130
00:06:56,040 --> 00:06:57,640
into a student's desk drawer

131
00:06:57,680 --> 00:06:59,340
without fear of being caught—

132
00:06:59,680 --> 00:07:02,750
that must have been done
by someone with a classroom key.

133
00:07:02,750 --> 00:07:03,510
There aren't many people

134
00:07:03,510 --> 00:07:05,640
who have keys to multiple classrooms,

135
00:07:06,230 --> 00:07:07,490
but you're one of them.

136
00:07:09,160 --> 00:07:09,990
Go on.

137
00:07:11,700 --> 00:07:14,030
One of the puzzles was a crossword puzzle,

138
00:07:14,280 --> 00:07:16,200
which happens to be your interest

139
00:07:16,230 --> 00:07:17,990
and something you're best at.

140
00:07:22,240 --> 00:07:24,190
"If I can stop one heart

141
00:07:24,190 --> 00:07:25,830
from breaking..."

142
00:07:26,660 --> 00:07:28,290
It was precisely this poem

143
00:07:29,310 --> 00:07:30,750
that convinced me

144
00:07:31,430 --> 00:07:33,030
you were the mystery person.

145
00:07:36,720 --> 00:07:37,680
Today,

146
00:07:38,820 --> 00:07:41,430
when you asked to
borrow that poetry collection,

147
00:07:41,430 --> 00:07:42,870
I already knew.

148
00:07:48,050 --> 00:07:50,010
Knowing the students inside and out

149
00:07:50,010 --> 00:07:51,740
wouldn't be difficult for you.

150
00:07:52,190 --> 00:07:54,700
But the mystery person knows me
to a degree

151
00:07:55,240 --> 00:07:57,300
that you couldn't possibly achieve.

152
00:07:58,430 --> 00:07:59,750
So I guess

153
00:08:02,470 --> 00:08:04,600
there's more than one mystery person.

154
00:08:07,480 --> 00:08:08,680
There's another one.

155
00:08:10,370 --> 00:08:11,980
Could it be my grandpa?

156
00:08:18,630 --> 00:08:20,360
You're just like your grandpa—

157
00:08:21,330 --> 00:08:23,750
playing chess to mess with
my train of thought.

158
00:08:23,750 --> 00:08:25,210
That's unsportsmanlike.

159
00:08:25,880 --> 00:08:27,460
That makes sense then.

160
00:08:29,330 --> 00:08:30,930
But I have one more question.

161
00:08:31,630 --> 00:08:33,480
Only internal staff can register for

162
00:08:33,480 --> 00:08:35,630
an email account at Hengjiu.

163
00:08:36,480 --> 00:08:37,150
So...

164
00:08:41,039 --> 00:08:43,070
Have you ever heard the boys

165
00:08:43,480 --> 00:08:45,940
talk about Coach Jiang
of the football team?

166
00:08:46,340 --> 00:08:47,520
Of course I have.

167
00:08:50,710 --> 00:08:52,780
Jiang had a son named Jiang Xun.

168
00:08:53,570 --> 00:08:54,770
He works at Hengjiu

169
00:08:55,490 --> 00:08:58,490
as the general manager's
administrative assistant.

170
00:08:58,790 --> 00:09:01,150
After Jiang passed away
due to an accident,

171
00:09:01,150 --> 00:09:04,590
he put all the pieces together
and figured out what had happened.

172
00:09:04,590 --> 00:09:05,480
This Jiang Xun

173
00:09:05,480 --> 00:09:07,940
was your grandfather's favorite disciple.

174
00:09:08,140 --> 00:09:09,990
While your grandfather was in hospital,

175
00:09:09,990 --> 00:09:12,230
he often went to visit him.

176
00:09:12,930 --> 00:09:14,260
Wanxing...

177
00:09:14,290 --> 00:09:16,480
When Wanxing was 5 or 6,

178
00:09:16,500 --> 00:09:17,500
she

179
00:09:17,550 --> 00:09:18,550
asked me all the time,

180
00:09:18,550 --> 00:09:23,670
"Grandpa, why is my name Wanxing
and not something about the moon?"

181
00:09:23,670 --> 00:09:25,030
I said, "Wanxing,

182
00:09:25,030 --> 00:09:26,080
there are many stars,

183
00:09:26,080 --> 00:09:27,640
but only one moon."

184
00:09:27,670 --> 00:09:29,270
She said she wanted to be the moon.

185
00:09:29,270 --> 00:09:31,320
I told her it was better to be a star.

186
00:09:33,480 --> 00:09:34,080
Darling.

187
00:09:34,840 --> 00:09:35,270
Here.

188
00:09:35,270 --> 00:09:36,720
I forgot to tell you.

189
00:09:36,720 --> 00:09:38,200
I don't feel like eating.

190
00:09:39,060 --> 00:09:40,150
Then you eat it.

191
00:09:40,150 --> 00:09:40,670
What?

192
00:09:40,670 --> 00:09:41,200
I...

193
00:09:41,600 --> 00:09:42,440
It's delicious.

194
00:09:42,440 --> 00:09:42,910
Come on,

195
00:09:43,070 --> 00:09:44,140
take it. Come on.

196
00:09:45,990 --> 00:09:47,270
Jiang Xun.

197
00:09:47,550 --> 00:09:49,280
Thank you for coming to see me

198
00:09:49,550 --> 00:09:51,810
and listening to me ramble on for so long.

199
00:09:52,320 --> 00:09:53,270
Pardon me.

200
00:09:53,270 --> 00:09:53,960
Pardon me.

201
00:09:53,960 --> 00:09:55,200
I'm your student.

202
00:09:55,840 --> 00:09:57,200
It's only natural.

203
00:09:57,840 --> 00:09:59,090
Actually, the one

204
00:09:59,280 --> 00:10:02,240
he's most worried about is Wanxing.

205
00:10:03,200 --> 00:10:04,550
Don't worry.

206
00:10:04,550 --> 00:10:06,150
Wanxing is such an outstanding person.

207
00:10:06,150 --> 00:10:07,320
She'll be fine.

208
00:10:13,340 --> 00:10:14,620
Time truly flies.

209
00:10:15,490 --> 00:10:18,550
It's already been a year
since your father passed away.

210
00:10:19,550 --> 00:10:21,000
If I could see him,

211
00:10:21,000 --> 00:10:23,080
I'd tell Jiang

212
00:10:23,080 --> 00:10:25,960
that he had a wonderful son.

213
00:10:26,250 --> 00:10:28,160
You have to thank me, you know?

214
00:10:30,240 --> 00:10:31,710
Sure. Thank you.

215
00:10:33,840 --> 00:10:35,440
Your grandpa and grandma

216
00:10:35,440 --> 00:10:37,720
wanted you to get back on your feet,

217
00:10:38,670 --> 00:10:40,200
while Jiang Xun

218
00:10:40,200 --> 00:10:42,420
wanted to carry on his father's legacy

219
00:10:42,440 --> 00:10:44,560
to keep the football team going.

220
00:10:45,440 --> 00:10:47,370
The two of them hit it off right away

221
00:10:47,450 --> 00:10:50,570
and came up with
the "mystery person" plan.

222
00:10:50,670 --> 00:10:52,550
We've made a decision.

223
00:10:52,550 --> 00:10:53,740
You carry it out.

224
00:10:54,320 --> 00:10:58,080
-God, the first step is the probate.
-The plan was missing an executor,

225
00:10:58,080 --> 00:10:59,270
so they asked me

226
00:10:59,600 --> 00:11:01,270
to take on that role.

227
00:11:01,600 --> 00:11:02,840
-It's "work hard."
-Oh, it's "work hard."

228
00:11:02,840 --> 00:11:04,270
Look at the way you wrote "hard."

229
00:11:04,090 --> 00:11:08,420
[Action Plan]

230
00:11:04,270 --> 00:11:08,720
Have Wanxing teach at Hongjing No. 8 High.

231
00:11:08,720 --> 00:11:09,320
Great. Applause.

232
00:11:09,320 --> 00:11:10,440
Great.

233
00:11:11,520 --> 00:11:13,580
[Wanxing, I'll be gone soon.]

234
00:11:14,480 --> 00:11:16,070
The first step of the plan

235
00:11:17,030 --> 00:11:19,360
was for your grandpa
to write you a letter,

236
00:11:19,440 --> 00:11:22,570
suggesting that you come to teach
at Hongjing No. 8 High.

237
00:11:22,620 --> 00:11:24,510
[Remember to eat well and live well.]

238
00:11:24,440 --> 00:11:25,600
And that letter

239
00:11:25,720 --> 00:11:27,670
set our mysterious plan in motion.

240
00:11:28,790 --> 00:11:29,670
First,

241
00:11:30,360 --> 00:11:31,960
it was to bring you
to Hongjing No. 8 High,

242
00:11:31,960 --> 00:11:34,820
so that the football team
could have a new backbone.

243
00:11:35,840 --> 00:11:36,670
Second,

244
00:11:37,270 --> 00:11:39,880
it was to help you
become part of the football team,

245
00:11:39,880 --> 00:11:43,080
so that you and the boys
could support and save each other.

246
00:11:47,200 --> 00:11:47,790
Look.

247
00:11:47,790 --> 00:11:48,590
This would do.

248
00:11:56,440 --> 00:11:58,630
First, that 100-time football lending card

249
00:11:58,630 --> 00:12:01,430
was meant to spark your curiosity
about football.

250
00:12:03,910 --> 00:12:04,670
Wonderful.

251
00:12:05,840 --> 00:12:07,360
"Start over from the beginning"—

252
00:12:07,360 --> 00:12:08,080
does this work?

253
00:12:08,080 --> 00:12:08,910
It needs to be more positive.

254
00:12:08,910 --> 00:12:09,840
"Dare to be the first."

255
00:12:09,840 --> 00:12:13,550
-Leave the kids some room for imagination.
-That's right.

256
00:12:13,840 --> 00:12:15,300
Cross it out. Cross it out.

257
00:12:15,580 --> 00:12:16,670
Second,

258
00:12:15,700 --> 00:12:20,120
[Make a great coup]

259
00:12:16,670 --> 00:12:18,230
the crossword puzzle

260
00:12:18,550 --> 00:12:20,910
was meant to give you a new understanding
of the football team.

261
00:12:20,910 --> 00:12:21,960
Let it dry a bit.

262
00:12:21,960 --> 00:12:23,000
Put it here.

263
00:12:27,980 --> 00:12:31,650
[Calculate the value of
Euler's totient function]

264
00:12:31,700 --> 00:12:34,030
[Calculate]

265
00:12:31,910 --> 00:12:34,200
The third was that mysterious map.

266
00:12:34,240 --> 00:12:36,500
It was meant to help you and the kids

267
00:12:36,530 --> 00:12:37,980
find a new home.

268
00:12:44,360 --> 00:12:45,890
Just take this place and...

269
00:12:46,080 --> 00:12:47,200
This...

270
00:12:52,740 --> 00:12:53,510
[Wanxing, I'll be gone soon. It's a shame]

271
00:12:53,530 --> 00:12:54,230
[we didn't get to see each other
one last time.]

272
00:12:58,380 --> 00:13:06,610
[Lin Xunya]

273
00:13:22,550 --> 00:13:26,510
Jiang and your grandfather both
passed away with unfulfilled concerns.

274
00:13:26,510 --> 00:13:27,360
So of course, Jiang Xun and I

275
00:13:27,360 --> 00:13:29,550
wanted to carry on with this

276
00:13:29,550 --> 00:13:31,440
and fulfill their final wishes—

277
00:13:32,080 --> 00:13:34,670
to let the lost Wanxing
and the helpless kids

278
00:13:35,350 --> 00:13:36,820
illuminate each other.

279
00:13:40,840 --> 00:13:42,320
I think as for Coach Wang,

280
00:13:42,320 --> 00:13:43,960
it was indeed an accident.

281
00:13:44,480 --> 00:13:45,670
But I still believe

282
00:13:46,360 --> 00:13:48,840
it was precisely because
you're such a nice person

283
00:13:48,840 --> 00:13:49,480
that God

284
00:13:49,480 --> 00:13:52,180
placed Wang Fa in this difficult chapter

285
00:13:52,260 --> 00:13:53,620
of your life.

286
00:14:01,400 --> 00:14:02,900
And finally, he told me

287
00:14:03,960 --> 00:14:05,870
that once you discovered the truth,

288
00:14:05,870 --> 00:14:08,470
there would be one final gift
for me to give you.

289
00:14:10,480 --> 00:14:11,600
He hoped to tell you

290
00:14:12,910 --> 00:14:14,780
about it himself

291
00:14:14,810 --> 00:14:16,120
in a happy place.

292
00:14:17,440 --> 00:14:18,200
Of course,

293
00:14:18,570 --> 00:14:21,700
Jiang Xun also had something
he wanted to say to the kids.

294
00:14:35,080 --> 00:14:36,550
Kids,

295
00:14:38,910 --> 00:14:40,080
I'm sorry.

296
00:14:41,480 --> 00:14:43,550
Your old man Jiang here

297
00:14:44,360 --> 00:14:45,320
has to...

298
00:14:46,030 --> 00:14:48,240
Has to break his promise.

299
00:14:49,470 --> 00:14:51,590
I promised

300
00:14:52,670 --> 00:14:56,550
I'd lead you to win the championship.

301
00:14:57,920 --> 00:14:59,350
But I...

302
00:15:01,320 --> 00:15:03,480
I won't be able to do it.

303
00:15:04,270 --> 00:15:06,360
I feel very guilty.

304
00:15:08,320 --> 00:15:10,150
In my heart,

305
00:15:11,030 --> 00:15:12,080
you guys

306
00:15:13,360 --> 00:15:16,230
have been champions all along.

307
00:15:17,550 --> 00:15:20,080
Fu Xinshu,

308
00:15:21,800 --> 00:15:23,800
Yu Ming,

309
00:15:27,190 --> 00:15:29,400
Zhi Hui,

310
00:15:32,430 --> 00:15:33,960
Zheng Ren,

311
00:15:34,600 --> 00:15:36,220
and...

312
00:15:36,670 --> 00:15:38,800
Zheng Feiyang,

313
00:15:40,970 --> 00:15:42,760
Qi Liang,

314
00:15:45,650 --> 00:15:47,340
Lin Lu,

315
00:15:48,750 --> 00:15:50,200
Qin Ao,

316
00:15:52,960 --> 00:15:55,320
Chen Jianghe,

317
00:15:57,720 --> 00:15:59,720
Feng Suo,

318
00:16:01,240 --> 00:16:03,670
and Jiang Tianyu.

319
00:16:04,840 --> 00:16:07,270
I will remember

320
00:16:07,270 --> 00:16:10,270
every single one of you.

321
00:16:11,790 --> 00:16:13,670
I hope

322
00:16:13,670 --> 00:16:15,550
that even without me,

323
00:16:16,310 --> 00:16:17,780
you guys...

324
00:16:18,930 --> 00:16:20,520
You guys will still

325
00:16:21,480 --> 00:16:23,080
continue to

326
00:16:23,910 --> 00:16:26,870
love football.

327
00:16:29,200 --> 00:16:31,030
Kids,

328
00:16:34,200 --> 00:16:35,200
good...

329
00:16:37,080 --> 00:16:37,960
Good...

330
00:16:40,440 --> 00:16:43,080
Goodbye.

331
00:16:44,600 --> 00:16:47,550
Goodbye.

332
00:16:52,150 --> 00:16:55,320
Goodbye.

333
00:17:07,380 --> 00:17:08,510
Hello, guys.

334
00:17:08,640 --> 00:17:11,680
I'm Jiang Xun, Coach Jiang's son.

335
00:17:13,109 --> 00:17:15,510
A little over 2 years ago—

336
00:17:16,069 --> 00:17:17,069
right around the time you guys

337
00:17:17,069 --> 00:17:18,730
first started at Hongjing No.8 High—

338
00:17:18,730 --> 00:17:20,260
my dad fell seriously ill.

339
00:17:20,290 --> 00:17:22,160
He remained unconscious for a long time,

340
00:17:22,160 --> 00:17:25,359
so I took him to Yongchuan,
where I worked, for treatment.

341
00:17:25,750 --> 00:17:26,640
During his time

342
00:17:26,640 --> 00:17:28,079
in the ICU,

343
00:17:28,290 --> 00:17:30,220
he never regained consciousness.

344
00:17:31,470 --> 00:17:34,390
Then, on the morning of
the day he passed away,

345
00:17:34,510 --> 00:17:36,720
he suddenly opened his eyes and told me

346
00:17:37,090 --> 00:17:39,150
he wanted to record a message for you.

347
00:17:40,940 --> 00:17:42,790
Which is the one you just saw.

348
00:17:45,310 --> 00:17:46,910
What I want to tell you is

349
00:17:48,790 --> 00:17:50,050
that your Coach Jiang,

350
00:17:51,270 --> 00:17:53,930
even during those days
when he was unconscious,

351
00:17:54,280 --> 00:17:56,610
never once thought about giving up on you.

352
00:18:14,790 --> 00:18:15,590
Is it all set?

353
00:18:18,110 --> 00:18:18,920
Wanxing.

354
00:18:20,350 --> 00:18:23,510
How's your life been going
at No. 8 High School?

355
00:18:24,270 --> 00:18:26,270
Have those kids on the football team

356
00:18:26,270 --> 00:18:28,550
been bothering you so much that

357
00:18:28,550 --> 00:18:31,070
you've had no time to think about me?

358
00:18:33,510 --> 00:18:35,270
I'm very happy.

359
00:18:36,270 --> 00:18:37,510
I know

360
00:18:38,070 --> 00:18:40,000
it might not be long—

361
00:18:40,590 --> 00:18:43,310
maybe just 3 months,

362
00:18:43,880 --> 00:18:45,440
or maybe longer.

363
00:18:46,270 --> 00:18:48,510
But I just know

364
00:18:48,510 --> 00:18:51,440
that you'll definitely see this video.

365
00:18:56,310 --> 00:18:59,160
You've been through a lot lately.

366
00:18:58,380 --> 00:19:04,060
♪ Waiting for a dark cloud
to pass by you ♪

367
00:19:00,700 --> 00:19:02,150
I believe

368
00:19:02,260 --> 00:19:04,740
you're definitely able to

369
00:19:04,650 --> 00:19:09,180
♪ Listen closely to its cries ♪

370
00:19:04,760 --> 00:19:06,930
eat well

371
00:19:06,960 --> 00:19:09,030
and live well.

372
00:19:10,310 --> 00:19:11,590
Are you

373
00:19:11,260 --> 00:19:16,360
♪ The heavy rain will wash away
your reflection ♪

374
00:19:12,480 --> 00:19:14,730
able to smile

375
00:19:14,750 --> 00:19:16,420
more often now?

376
00:19:17,190 --> 00:19:22,620
♪ And carry it toward distant scenery ♪

377
00:19:21,430 --> 00:19:22,350
Wanxing.

378
00:19:23,030 --> 00:19:24,050
In the future,

379
00:19:24,190 --> 00:19:29,900
♪ Every experience has its meaning ♪

380
00:19:24,240 --> 00:19:27,790
there will be many times
when you feel lost and unsure.

381
00:19:28,510 --> 00:19:30,550
But I believe

382
00:19:30,640 --> 00:19:35,440
♪ Scene by scene, they come together
to form who I am ♪

383
00:19:31,000 --> 00:19:32,920
that you know.

384
00:19:33,510 --> 00:19:35,880
You know that I love you.

385
00:19:36,550 --> 00:19:38,590
I've always been here,

386
00:19:37,110 --> 00:19:42,260
♪ Even the wounds
that leave behind their marks ♪

387
00:19:39,720 --> 00:19:41,510
and I always will be.

388
00:19:42,370 --> 00:19:46,280
I'm just staying by your side
in a different way now.

389
00:19:43,240 --> 00:19:48,410
♪ Have taught me how to heal myself ♪

390
00:19:49,260 --> 00:19:55,150
♪ The love I have given,
the love I have received ♪

391
00:19:55,870 --> 00:20:01,640
♪ Every one of them gives me the strength
not to fear being hurt ♪

392
00:20:02,320 --> 00:20:07,930
♪ Let my tears be carried away,
back into the ocean ♪

393
00:20:05,310 --> 00:20:06,550
Turns out Coach Jiang

394
00:20:07,750 --> 00:20:09,400
never gave up on us.

395
00:20:08,780 --> 00:20:14,020
♪ And blown toward flowers
blooming far away ♪

396
00:20:10,270 --> 00:20:11,830
For Coach Jiang

397
00:20:12,790 --> 00:20:14,880
and Ms. Lin's grandparents,

398
00:20:15,080 --> 00:20:20,660
♪ I fill the blank spaces of life
with colors ♪

399
00:20:16,790 --> 00:20:18,310
we must win.

400
00:20:21,400 --> 00:20:27,140
♪ My dreams are not afraid to awaken;
they continue to exist ♪

401
00:20:27,920 --> 00:20:33,980
♪ I go beyond the dark clouds
and feel the haze disperse ♪

402
00:20:34,580 --> 00:20:40,280
♪ Let me understand myself more clearly ♪

403
00:20:43,620 --> 00:20:44,900
Alright, gather the balls.

404
00:20:44,900 --> 00:20:45,550
Get ready to run.

405
00:20:45,550 --> 00:20:46,160
Okay.

406
00:20:46,160 --> 00:20:47,380
-It's her.
-It's her.

407
00:20:47,400 --> 00:20:48,000
It's her.

408
00:20:48,000 --> 00:20:49,510
So it's her.

409
00:20:52,110 --> 00:20:54,840
Yeah, I wouldn't have known
if you didn't tell me.

410
00:20:56,110 --> 00:20:57,030
She's such a homewrecker.

411
00:20:57,030 --> 00:20:58,960
-So it was her you were talking about?
-Yeah, it's her.

412
00:20:58,960 --> 00:20:59,720
-What was that?
-Shut up!

413
00:20:59,720 --> 00:21:00,270
What do you want?

414
00:21:00,270 --> 00:21:00,920
-What's wrong with you?
-Shut up!

415
00:21:00,920 --> 00:21:01,510
What are you looking at?

416
00:21:01,510 --> 00:21:02,240
-What do you think you're doing?
-Alright, alright.

417
00:21:02,240 --> 00:21:03,160
Anything you want to say?

418
00:21:03,160 --> 00:21:04,690
-Let's go.
-Yeah, let's go.

419
00:21:05,140 --> 00:21:06,010
Ms. Lin,

420
00:21:06,040 --> 00:21:06,930
ignore them.

421
00:21:07,580 --> 00:21:08,410
I'm okay.

422
00:21:11,510 --> 00:21:12,370
Go run.

423
00:21:14,600 --> 00:21:15,130
Let's go.

424
00:21:20,790 --> 00:21:21,520
Are you okay?

425
00:21:23,730 --> 00:21:25,300
After all this time,

426
00:21:25,330 --> 00:21:26,990
I've come to understand this:

427
00:21:27,160 --> 00:21:29,450
the rumors won't stop.

428
00:21:29,850 --> 00:21:31,850
But until the truth comes to light,

429
00:21:32,250 --> 00:21:34,380
I need to learn to stop blaming myself.

430
00:22:01,540 --> 00:22:02,340
You mean

431
00:22:03,300 --> 00:22:05,560
you had guessed it was Xiang Zi all along?

432
00:22:07,010 --> 00:22:09,150
I never tried to verify it.

433
00:22:10,100 --> 00:22:11,130
Before,

434
00:22:12,240 --> 00:22:14,500
I didn't even have the courage to face it.

435
00:22:16,160 --> 00:22:18,960
There were two pieces of evidence
used to frame me.

436
00:22:19,710 --> 00:22:21,750
When Professor Shu committed suicide,

437
00:22:21,750 --> 00:22:24,410
there was a photo from my trip
tucked in his book.

438
00:22:25,610 --> 00:22:26,960
Director Jia from the department

439
00:22:26,960 --> 00:22:28,590
also used that very photo

440
00:22:29,040 --> 00:22:31,770
to question my relationship
with Professor Shu.

441
00:22:31,830 --> 00:22:33,130
I had many copies of that set of photos

442
00:22:33,130 --> 00:22:34,610
printed back then.

443
00:22:34,890 --> 00:22:35,890
I guess

444
00:22:36,990 --> 00:22:40,790
the one they found was taken from
those copies without my knowledge.

445
00:22:40,800 --> 00:22:41,590
Then,

446
00:22:44,110 --> 00:22:45,710
what was the other evidence?

447
00:22:51,860 --> 00:22:55,860
It was a video supposedly showing
me going to Professor Shu's hotel room

448
00:22:56,540 --> 00:22:59,540
during the
China Psychological Research Symposium.

449
00:23:00,550 --> 00:23:02,210
Hotel surveillance footage?

450
00:23:02,580 --> 00:23:04,510
The person in that video wasn't me,

451
00:23:06,220 --> 00:23:08,020
but they were dressed and styled

452
00:23:08,580 --> 00:23:10,300
exactly like I was.

453
00:23:10,840 --> 00:23:12,320
No matter how I argued,

454
00:23:12,340 --> 00:23:13,940
they wouldn't believe me,

455
00:23:13,970 --> 00:23:18,500
and they said my attempts to defend myself
only made me look even more suspicious.

456
00:23:19,050 --> 00:23:20,640
Do you still have

457
00:23:21,750 --> 00:23:22,550
that video?

458
00:23:26,200 --> 00:23:27,680
After it happened,

459
00:23:28,880 --> 00:23:31,140
I tried to ask the hotel for that footage.

460
00:23:31,240 --> 00:23:32,110
They told me

461
00:23:32,880 --> 00:23:35,340
the surveillance footage
had already been overwritten,

462
00:23:35,340 --> 00:23:36,960
and that they couldn't let me have it

463
00:23:36,960 --> 00:23:38,330
due to guest privacy.

464
00:23:44,320 --> 00:23:45,700
Hotel surveillance footage

465
00:23:45,700 --> 00:23:47,420
couldn't possibly have been overwritten
that quickly.

466
00:23:47,420 --> 00:23:49,020
There must be more to this.

467
00:23:51,040 --> 00:23:52,280
Besides the hotel,

468
00:23:52,670 --> 00:23:53,600
was that video

469
00:23:53,990 --> 00:23:55,520
circulated anywhere else?

470
00:24:00,720 --> 00:24:02,420
It circulated on the school forum

471
00:24:02,420 --> 00:24:03,830
for a while back then,

472
00:24:04,750 --> 00:24:06,950
but the original post has been deleted.

473
00:24:16,310 --> 00:24:17,040
Don't worry.

474
00:24:18,550 --> 00:24:20,810
We'll find the original source somehow.

475
00:24:21,550 --> 00:24:23,150
We'll figure something out.

476
00:24:28,130 --> 00:24:28,890
Back then,

477
00:24:29,170 --> 00:24:31,200
I was trapped in a struggle
to prove my innocence.

478
00:24:31,200 --> 00:24:31,810
This time,

479
00:24:32,470 --> 00:24:33,890
I'll uncover the truth

480
00:24:33,090 --> 00:24:34,280
[Director Jia]

481
00:24:34,380 --> 00:24:35,440
and reclaim the justice
that was taken from me.

482
00:24:34,430 --> 00:24:37,470
[Hello, Director Jia.]

483
00:24:37,630 --> 00:24:39,100
Hello, Director Jia.

484
00:24:39,320 --> 00:24:40,530
This is Lin Wanxing.

485
00:24:41,540 --> 00:24:43,910
I'd like to ask you about something

486
00:24:41,680 --> 00:24:44,120
[Director Jia]

487
00:24:43,950 --> 00:24:45,810
concerning that previous video.

488
00:24:55,750 --> 00:24:56,240
Coach.

489
00:24:56,240 --> 00:24:57,070
Ms. Lin.

490
00:24:57,400 --> 00:24:58,550
We're here to deliver food.

491
00:24:58,550 --> 00:24:59,350
So early?

492
00:24:59,350 --> 00:25:01,070
Isn't your class in the evening?

493
00:25:01,070 --> 00:25:03,680
We just wanted to see
if there's anything we can do to help.

494
00:25:03,680 --> 00:25:04,270
We just received the video

495
00:25:04,270 --> 00:25:06,160
that was used to frame Ms. Lin back then.

496
00:25:06,160 --> 00:25:08,070
We're trying to see
if we can find any flaws.

497
00:25:08,070 --> 00:25:09,310
Really? Let's do it together then.

498
00:25:09,310 --> 00:25:10,640
Many hands make light work.

499
00:25:10,640 --> 00:25:11,440
That's right.

500
00:25:21,880 --> 00:25:22,600
Ms. Lin,

501
00:25:22,630 --> 00:25:23,430
this...

502
00:25:23,680 --> 00:25:25,500
Although that person dressed like me,

503
00:25:25,500 --> 00:25:26,920
it really wasn't me.

504
00:25:26,950 --> 00:25:28,380
Xiang Zi knows you very well,

505
00:25:28,380 --> 00:25:30,060
so it wouldn't be difficult for him
to impersonate you.

506
00:25:30,060 --> 00:25:31,340
But this video alone

507
00:25:31,360 --> 00:25:33,090
isn't enough to prove
that the person in it was Xiang Zi.

508
00:25:33,090 --> 00:25:34,140
There must be some inconsistency.

509
00:25:34,140 --> 00:25:35,270
Let's keep looking.

510
00:25:45,410 --> 00:25:46,170
Look.

511
00:25:52,270 --> 00:25:52,960
Before going in,

512
00:25:52,960 --> 00:25:54,480
did he turn his neck left and right

513
00:25:54,480 --> 00:25:55,400
and then pat it?

514
00:25:55,420 --> 00:25:56,310
Indeed.

515
00:25:56,940 --> 00:25:58,130
If you don't look closely,

516
00:25:58,130 --> 00:25:59,820
you'd think he was fixing his hair.

517
00:25:59,820 --> 00:26:00,640
And because he had long hair,

518
00:26:00,640 --> 00:26:01,700
it wasn't obvious.

519
00:26:01,750 --> 00:26:02,580
It's him.

520
00:26:02,580 --> 00:26:06,450
[Yuanyuan Tutoring Class]

521
00:26:02,600 --> 00:26:04,310
That's one of his habitual gestures.

522
00:26:04,310 --> 00:26:06,590
He does this whenever he gets nervous.

523
00:26:06,610 --> 00:26:07,920
Then what are we waiting for?

524
00:26:07,920 --> 00:26:08,790
Let's just have the police arrest him.

525
00:26:08,790 --> 00:26:09,320
Exactly.

526
00:26:10,650 --> 00:26:12,240
But a mere habitual gesture

527
00:26:12,270 --> 00:26:14,200
isn't enough to serve as evidence.

528
00:26:16,110 --> 00:26:17,550
Then what should we do next?

529
00:26:17,550 --> 00:26:19,350
How do we collect more evidence?

530
00:26:21,330 --> 00:26:22,260
Let me have a try.

531
00:26:22,720 --> 00:26:23,640
I'll go online and check

532
00:26:23,640 --> 00:26:25,570
if there's any other information.

533
00:26:27,500 --> 00:26:28,360
Make some room.

534
00:26:29,890 --> 00:26:33,350
[Yuanyuan Tutoring Class]

535
00:26:36,700 --> 00:26:39,120
[Console]

536
00:26:39,340 --> 00:26:40,860
You know how to do this?

537
00:26:40,890 --> 00:26:41,870
This is called web scraping.

538
00:26:41,870 --> 00:26:43,790
It automatically gathers
publicly available information online,

539
00:26:43,790 --> 00:26:44,920
like the school website

540
00:26:44,920 --> 00:26:46,480
and videos posted by
student organizations.

541
00:26:46,480 --> 00:26:48,770
Since they're public,
accessing them is completely legal.

542
00:26:48,770 --> 00:26:50,680
[Console]

543
00:26:50,780 --> 00:26:52,110
[Yuanyuan Tutoring Class]

544
00:26:57,030 --> 00:26:58,240
Will this really work?

545
00:26:58,240 --> 00:27:00,270
I could finish a dungeon by now.

546
00:27:01,200 --> 00:27:03,930
With your poor skills,
you'd be dead in 3 minutes.

547
00:27:08,660 --> 00:27:09,460
[The Educational Delegation
from Yongchuan University]

548
00:27:09,480 --> 00:27:10,250
[Visited and Extended Warm Greetings
to Overseas Students in the UK]

549
00:27:13,250 --> 00:27:14,330
Gather around.

550
00:27:15,640 --> 00:27:16,970
It's nice to see you all.

551
00:27:17,800 --> 00:27:19,710
We'll need you to attend
tomorrow's seminar.

552
00:27:17,890 --> 00:27:19,810
[The Educational Delegation
from Yongchuan University]

553
00:27:19,830 --> 00:27:21,620
[Visited and Extended Warm Greetings
to Overseas Students in the UK]

554
00:27:20,440 --> 00:27:21,000
Okay.

555
00:27:21,000 --> 00:27:21,750
And

556
00:27:22,060 --> 00:27:23,620
if possible, please share

557
00:27:23,650 --> 00:27:26,910
your experiences studying abroad
over the past few years.

558
00:27:27,880 --> 00:27:28,930
[The Educational Delegation
from Yongchuan University]

559
