Is it just because
her father is the director?

840
00:40:20,840 --> 00:40:21,800
Xiang Zi.

841
00:40:22,510 --> 00:40:24,140
Recommendation selections

842
00:40:24,170 --> 00:40:25,900
evaluate research competence,

843
00:40:25,900 --> 00:40:27,010
academic achievements,

844
00:40:27,010 --> 00:40:28,280
and long-term potential

845
00:40:28,280 --> 00:40:29,880
comprehensively.

846
00:40:30,910 --> 00:40:32,880
Lin Wanxing truly stands out

847
00:40:32,900 --> 00:40:34,630
in all these aspects.

848
00:40:36,030 --> 00:40:37,230
Stands out?

849
00:40:37,600 --> 00:40:39,120
In what way?

850
00:40:39,150 --> 00:40:41,070
She's nothing but a flirt.

851
00:40:42,280 --> 00:40:44,180
I don't want to hear

852
00:40:44,210 --> 00:40:45,920
such baseless rumors anymore.

853
00:40:45,920 --> 00:40:46,730
Xiang Zi.

854
00:40:46,750 --> 00:40:47,980
You should know

855
00:40:48,040 --> 00:40:49,640
that integrity is paramount

856
00:40:51,100 --> 00:40:52,910
in academia.

857
00:41:00,260 --> 00:41:01,520
What are you implying?

858
00:41:05,040 --> 00:41:06,690
Are your thesis data

859
00:41:07,360 --> 00:41:09,120
100% authentic?

860
00:41:17,020 --> 00:41:19,350
I'll never grant the recommendation spot

861
00:41:19,640 --> 00:41:22,040
to someone guilty of academic misconduct.

862
00:41:32,200 --> 00:41:33,410
Professor.

863
00:41:34,510 --> 00:41:36,590
Are you saying that in academia,

864
00:41:38,100 --> 00:41:39,850
integrity comes first?

865
00:41:40,500 --> 00:41:41,140
Yes.

866
00:41:45,230 --> 00:41:47,320
Well, if that's the case...

867
00:41:53,310 --> 00:41:55,230
Physicians cannot heal themselves.

868
00:41:55,230 --> 00:41:59,010
[Sertraline Hydrochloride Tablets]

869
00:42:01,380 --> 00:42:02,480
Professor.

870
00:42:03,600 --> 00:42:05,890
Your mental state has been

871
00:42:26,100 --> 00:42:27,500
rather unstable lately.

872
00:42:28,360 --> 00:42:29,190
Get out!

873
00:42:35,120 --> 00:42:38,210
As the most authoritative mentor
in psychology,

874
00:42:36,730 --> 00:42:44,480
[Certificate of Honor]

875
00:42:38,510 --> 00:42:40,510
can you truly call yourself honest?

876
00:42:41,190 --> 00:42:43,630
Would you dare let me
look into your paper

877
00:42:43,630 --> 00:42:44,630
from 20 years ago?

878
00:42:46,340 --> 00:42:50,000
[Certificate of Honor]

879
00:42:48,800 --> 00:42:50,630
You built your reputation
as a leading expert

880
00:42:50,630 --> 00:42:53,090
in this field
through academic misconduct.

881
00:42:56,180 --> 00:42:57,580
Where is your integrity?

882
00:42:59,230 --> 00:43:00,710
How did you find out?

883
00:43:04,470 --> 00:43:05,670
I happened to

884
00:43:06,960 --> 00:43:08,360
pick a research topic

885
00:43:08,760 --> 00:43:10,630
similar to yours,

886
00:43:10,680 --> 00:43:12,390
so I thoroughly looked into

887
00:43:12,410 --> 00:43:14,180
your profile

888
00:43:14,200 --> 00:43:17,310
and studied every single paper
you have published.

889
00:43:17,360 --> 00:43:19,800
I told you, I'm a very hardworking person.

890
00:43:20,070 --> 00:43:20,990
Professor.

891
00:43:21,480 --> 00:43:23,210
Surely you understand that

892
00:43:23,240 --> 00:43:24,280
every action

893
00:43:24,840 --> 00:43:26,510
leaves traces behind.

894
00:43:32,940 --> 00:43:34,580
Back during your postdoctoral research,

895
00:43:34,580 --> 00:43:36,080
you hit a wall

896
00:43:36,340 --> 00:43:37,960
and desperately needed published papers.

897
00:43:37,960 --> 00:43:39,970
If I hadn't chanced upon

898
00:43:39,990 --> 00:43:42,220
a relevant thesis,

899
00:43:42,340 --> 00:43:44,540
I might never have discovered

900
00:43:45,040 --> 00:43:47,570
that a set of experimental data
you published

901
00:43:47,960 --> 00:43:49,960
was plagiarized from someone else.

902
00:43:59,440 --> 00:44:01,900
Give me Lin Wanxing's recommendation spot,

903
00:44:02,430 --> 00:44:04,590
and I'll keep this secret for you.

904
00:44:05,690 --> 00:44:06,890
What do you say?

905
00:44:10,910 --> 00:44:12,910
You only have 3 days.

906
00:44:52,560 --> 00:44:53,500
-Hello, Professor.
-Hello, Professor.

907
00:44:53,500 --> 00:44:54,230
Hello.

908
00:44:56,890 --> 00:44:58,750
-Professor.
-Hello, Professor.

909
00:45:01,810 --> 00:45:02,930
Hello, Professor.

910
00:45:06,100 --> 00:45:07,250
Professor Shu.

911
00:45:07,940 --> 00:45:09,400
Have you made up your mind?

912
00:45:11,630 --> 00:45:13,330
A reminder—

913
00:45:13,800 --> 00:45:15,470
you've only got 2 days left.

